同藍井艾露有冇關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵依個人比侮辱左藍井<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解都有個井字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢癡線佬黎 影衰哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbf34ed2e4485ccf9819b46e4b063098ae0c28d","tid":51762,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"你同藍井咩關係"},{"pid":"adfa4f630ea33c880cab01d2a3433f51222a607e","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你同藍井咩關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藍井=我心靈支柱"},{"pid":"c1c603a2e87db35f9963f73bed667fd4747ef04a","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd297baa107e6b9b234c709ab62b8a339e359b2d","tid":51762,"uid":33681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"各方面分別洗左幾錢"},{"pid":"79dd3e6d438bfdecf8738d8b39b54c9530a3cd80","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各方面分別洗左幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實質價錢計唔到 <br />\n<br />\n應該有5-8萬左右<br />\n<br />\ncd 周邊（ 寫真 衫等等）<br />\n仲有睇live 一共睇左佢5場live"},{"pid":"c4e799ca2c13fafb434ad270340fedc657dff531","tid":51762,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"為左佢飛過幾次日本?<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講下自己有幾巨?"},{"pid":"eef056aaf71023c3070a9a7587a164a3f03cbd83","tid":51762,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"最中意同最唔中意佢邊首歌"},{"pid":"789b22623d11a3f6dc6403b056391d1b2fda76f5","tid":51762,"uid":33681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"來緊轉推邊個？"},{"pid":"9d5e6aa40de46e6f26e750d81a4eebacd53e8bb0","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來緊轉推邊個？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一日未宣布引退都唔會轉<br />\n加上好多歌手把聲都唔太鐘意<br />\n最多每個歌手都鐘意一兩首歌 好小首首都鐘意"},{"pid":"9a8624e698bd51414f8ad681ab6f7f3488e8fd26","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左佢飛過幾次日本?<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講下自己有幾巨?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3次 <br />\n<br />\n每日都要聽下佢啲歌先安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特登為左聽得明佢啲歌學日文<br />\n<br />\n差唔多買齊佢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二次元毒撚變左做三次元毒撚"},{"pid":"daa0d7b30aef1da39bc280a099989e07530650a7","tid":51762,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:32:43.000Z","msg":"推介幾首歌"},{"pid":"0ae9ddce74cc16d081d89b8e5e288fbdbbfc55e9","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最中意同最唔中意佢邊首歌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鐘意Accentier<br />\n歌詞最有意思 未必最好聽 但最鐘意<br />\n<br />\n初出道專輯有啲冷門歌都唔太鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdedc7ca1fcdbc8fcd1c9235d64111e7fbad8046","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推介幾首歌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱門歌唔洗推介啦<br />\n<br />\nA New Day <br />\n夢の終わり<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1ff6b479b0e4316bfebc795fe98b7c96a1e293","tid":51762,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:08:42.000Z","msg":"幾時轉會"},{"pid":"5e8dd68374eadfdfeee63754537a6e132b67c9e7","tid":5