24T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢其實拍左幾多露點/毛既寫真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇數過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有無對過佢既寫真打丁？<br />\n<br />\n有無佢既av?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔係av 只係寫真/尺寸大啲既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13f4bf5235f5c57a81b994e427a50d1d16f0c6a","tid":51762,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0035c2cc9d35bb891dbfe75f46168daecc27bb14","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有無對過佢既寫真打丁？<br />\n<br />\n有無佢既av?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有唔係av 只係寫真/尺寸大啲既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無睇哂<br />\n只係露點毛定係有三點盡露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢可以由個時去到而家咁既成就真係好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好似好多日本既女歌手/明星都有拍呢d寫真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都冇睇哂 好似只係差啲露兩點 唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有佢一出道果時就比人爆依單野出黎 <br />\n好過上到高峰先比人爆啦<br />\n所以我都好認同你咁講 仲可以去到咁既成就好堅<br />\n好欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢都叫實現左夢想架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6599015bbf99b2e0bd0afb89c4f9a7c8045781e","tid":51762,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"藍井艾露係雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb04bea82a19d849f8d010e50fd4bf125ed1cbd6","tid":51762,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dccefc20a624a645c2f06d9ab6991a996931d9dc","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無睇哂<br />\n只係露點毛定係有三點盡露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢可以由個時去到而家咁既成就真係好堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好似好多日本既女歌手/明星都有拍呢d寫真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都冇睇哂 好似只係差啲露兩點 唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有佢一出道果時就比人爆依單野出黎 <br />\n好過上到高峰先比人爆啦<br />\n所以我都好認同你咁講 仲可以去到咁既成就好堅<br />\n好欣賞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢都叫實現左夢想架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實日本比其他地方比較接受到呢d?<br />\n<br />\n可能因為好多女出道時都會拍呢d搏上位</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一出道比人爆出黎 一定易接受啲既<br />\n接受唔到都唔做佢fans"},{"pid":"3355c881bd312e60a029c1a9c7984eaef7a994f8","tid":51762,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍井艾露係雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老母做緊雞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你第時個女都要做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee35c5422a31c995d63564e566f153366f65bd2","tid":51762,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:38:17.000Z","